<emphasis id="3285EAA6FFCA8A2CF695F2FDF6FAD4E0" bold="true" box="[2393,2431,3420,3459]" pageId="5" pageNumber="284">in</emphasis>
coastal Northern, 
<emphasis id="3285EAA6FFCA8A2CF52FF2FDF404D4E0" box="[2787,2945,3420,3459]" italics="true" pageId="5" pageNumber="284">Western</emphasis>
, and 
<collectingRegion id="C235F856FFCA8A2CF427F2FDF36CD4E0" box="[3051,3305,3420,3459]" country="South Africa" name="Eastern Cape" pageId="5" pageNumber="284">Eastern Cape</collectingRegion>
provinces. Possibly enters coastal SW 
<collectingCountry id="78E67624FFCA8A2CF6AFF231F58DD4D4" box="[2403,2568,3472,3511]" name="Namibia" pageId="5" pageNumber="284">Namibia</collectingCountry>
, although this has 
